snippet.title: Doors of Insanity: ReOpened | The Mix Fall Showcase Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist Now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2860020/Doors_of_Insanity_ReOpened/

Doors of Insanity: ReOpened is a total reimagining of OneShark’s original Doors of Insanity, with new mechanics, cards, enemies, and more created by a small and passionate team in Neon Doctrine. 

Fans of roguelite deckbuilders will feel right at home in this loving tribute... But RPG equipment, mechanics, and more will keep them on their toes!
